{"tid":266971,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"掟屎咁大整蠱?     大埔青年褲中招","createTime":"2017-06-02T01:47:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-02T04:34:04.000Z","uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"661cc192cc57b2fbf2977530224b685bf5b9d8d8","tid":266971,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T01:47:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170602/large/1496367410_3f12.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170602%2Flarge%2F1496367410_3f12.jpg&h=4017fbf6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大埔太和邨2期商場對開，早上6時許，19歲姓陳青年在上址與友人傾談期間，突有一堆啡色物體從天而降，並發出陣陣異味，陳一望驚見一堆疑似糞便物體沾在其褲子上，嚇得報警求助，警員到場上門逐層搜索，惟未有發現，陳毋須送院，事後返家清洗穢物。事件中暫無人被捕。"},{"pid":"e61c7712b4962672b85b94f42db08fc8147637ca","tid":266971,"uid":28831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T01:48:36.000Z","msg":"哪裡來的屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"541682c3bcd8620540b7fca9266c8df2d0c2f259","tid":266971,"uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T02:11:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://whatscap.ristury.com/java/WhatsCAP/content/photo/v1/74186_WM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwhatscap.ristury.com%2Fjava%2FWhatsCAP%2Fcontent%2Fphoto%2Fv1%2F74186_WM.jpg&h=5639a9da&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"51ca93ff74b93787dc1e6a95f0f8a27503dcc819","tid":266971,"uid":55386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T03:29:15.000Z","msg":"太和撚表示 好不安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"711fb073185f5e10f036869afb5e12e3fd540d99","tid":266971,"uid":106065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T03:32:38.000Z","msg":"條褲有屎，根本係自己瀨<img src=\"/assets/fa